=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describes the maintenance window for a thin client device.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ApplyTimeOf => Str

The option to set the maintenance window during the device local time
or Universal Coordinated Time (UTC).


=head2 DaysOfTheWeek => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The days of the week during which the maintenance window is open.


=head2 EndTimeHour => Int

The hour for the maintenance window end (C<00>-C<23>).


=head2 EndTimeMinute => Int

The minutes for the maintenance window end (C<00>-C<59>).


=head2 StartTimeHour => Int

The hour for the maintenance window start (C<00>-C<23>).


=head2 StartTimeMinute => Int

The minutes past the hour for the maintenance window start
(C<00>-C<59>).


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Type => Str

An option to select the default or custom maintenance window.



